metadata.name: Predator Oil & Gas Holdings Plc
metadata.description: Predator Oil & Gas Holdings Plc, through its subsidiaries, operates as an oil and gas company in Africa, Europe, and the Caribbean. It builds a diversified portfolio of oil and gas interests with the focus on Enhanced Oil Recovery opportunities using carbon dioxide injection in Trinidad; and exploration and appraisal gas assets in offshore Ireland and onshore Morocco. Predator Oil & Gas Holdings Plc was incorporated in 2017 and is based in Saint Helier, Jersey.
